{"tid":2374583,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"倉務員藏噴漆擬噴Share of voice鼓勵年青人 今認罪保釋候判","createTime":"2021-01-21T10:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T12:22:31.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f212ebc8f3cd3544aeee0c842187c51efae69703","tid":2374583,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:39:52.000Z","msg":"有民間團體去年5月10日發起「全民覺醒 林鄭下台 九龍大遊行」，警方拒絕發不反對通知書。當日警方在油麻地截查19歲兼職倉務員，在其背囊檢獲兩支噴漆，他<span class=\"red\">警誡下承認打算在附近建築物用噴漆噴</span>上「S.O.V」（Share of voice）。倉務員今承認管有物品意圖損壞財產罪，辯方求情稱被告望為年輕人發聲才犯案，望能輕判。<br />\n<br />\n主任裁判官<span class=\"red\">嚴舜儀</span>決定先索閱被告鄧**（20歲）的感化及社會服務令報告才判刑，案件押後至下月3日，被告准保釋候判。"},{"pid":"9e670f9a57cc360472d9a40688baa6a5b26167a2","tid":2374583,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:40:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210121/QTCQ6P7C2RGVVGT3PQKBHEAOOY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210121%2FQTCQ6P7C2RGVVGT3PQKBHEAOOY%2F&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcMbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=b0f35f36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210121%2FQTCQ6P7C2RGVVGT3PQKBHEAOOY%2F&h=3e865c67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210121/QTCQ6P7C2RGVVGT3PQKBHEAOOY/</a>"},{"pid":"13c6b7c8215994a329d85592daaa6760b4910ca9","tid":2374583,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9134c40b58fbac0a1bf357337366fa87011299","tid":2374583,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:55:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /